            "body": "<p>You can make use of <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/lang/StringBuilder.html#reverse%28%29\">StringBuilder#reverse()<\/a> method like this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String reverse = new StringBuilder(new String(letters)).reverse().toString();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
