            "score": 4,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1456003728,
            "creation_date": 1456003728,
            "body": "<p>`<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>//not only prints the reverse order, but creates new char array with chars in desired order\nchar[] letters = {'e', 'v', 'o', 'l', '4'};\nint i = letters.length - 1, j = 0;\nchar[] let = new char[letters.length];\nwhile(i &gt;= 0){\n     let[j] = letters[i];\n     i--;\n     j++;\n}\nfor (char c : let){\n     System.out.print(c);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>`<\/p>\n\n<p>output:\n4love<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 35529280,
            "question_id": 13827654
        },
